metadata.description:
You are the product of countless tiny decisions taken over the course of your life. Stitched is an attempt to visualize oneâ€™s current self as a product of the myriad forking paths available to us. The animated version is available for view at

Stitched is generative art coded in p5.js, inspired by The Garden of Forking Paths by Borges and stylistically by French and Russian Impressionists, and Autoglyphs by Larva Labs.
